<plot>Casey isn't cool. He's not a geek either. He's a limbo kid. Everyone in school knows he has a crush on the popular Harper, but no one is prepared for Harper's startling confession, especially not Casey. I REALLY, REALLY LIKE YOU is a short romantic tragedy about playing it cool in middle school. Set in an urban alternative junior high school, this brief, but resonant tragedy explores themes of shockingly requited love and human foolishness.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?252987</url></doc>
